cs.GT, cs.EC, cs.LG, cs.CE, cs.DS 

This paper deals with the design of auctions, which is a topic in game theory (cs.GT) and mechanism design (cs.EC). The focus is on maximizing societal welfare, which involves optimizing the allocation of resources (cs.CE) and balancing the interests of multiple parties (cs.LG). The paper also involves analyzing strategic behavior and equilibrium outcomes (cs.DS).
